- content_for :title, 'Al Kader Shriners'

.hero
  = image_tag('hero_202002.jpg', alt: 'Fun with a Purpose', class: 'img-fluid w-100')
  .hero__lead-container
    .container
      .text-center.py-3
        %h1.pb-0.text-white Fun with a Purpose

.bg-caution.py-3
  .container
    .text-center
      %h2.text-white Refer a Child in Need to Shriners Hospital for Children
      = link_to('https://www.shrinershospitalsforchildren.org/shc/refer-a-patient',
                class: 'btn bt-lg btn-danger mt-4') do
        .h4.my-0.py-0
          Refer a Child

.pt-5
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-8
        %h1.py-3.text-center East West Shrine Game Apparel
        %p.lead
          The East West Shrine Game Committee would like to announce to the Nobles that we now have
          an online store for ordering Game Apparel. All Profits still get submitted to the
          committee and then in turn to the hospital.

        %p
          We encourage the Nobles and Families to Order from the following link as we strive to
          reduce overhead in our merchandise trailer. The other huge benefit to this is that
          nobles can order year round and do not have to be at the game to get apparel like the
          Shriner Leather Lettermans Jacket.
        .d-flex.justify-content-center
          = link_to('Shop Now!',
                    'https://www.titanbiz.co/sr/1641664',
                    class: 'btn btn-lg btn-danger mt-3 mb-5 mb-md-3')
      .col-md-4
        = image_tag('shop_game_apparel.jpg',
                      alt: 'East-West Shrine Game Apparel',
                      class: 'img-fluid')
.pt-5
  .container
    .card-group
      .card.bg-light
        .card-body
          = image_tag('card_oasis_2020_08.jpg',
                      alt: 'Oasis Cover',
                      class: 'img-fluid border border-primary')
        .card-footer
          = link_to('Oasis Newsletters',
                    oasis_path(trailing_slash: true),
                    class: 'btn btn-block btn-outline-primary')
      .card.bg-primary
        .card-body
          = image_tag('card_event_space.png', alt: 'Shrine Center', class: 'img-fluid')
        .card-footer
          = link_to('Rent Our Facility',
                    facility_rental_path(trailing_slash: true),
                    class: 'btn btn-block btn-caution')
      .card.bg-light
        .card-body
          = image_tag('card_event_calendar.jpg', alt: 'Shrine Center', class: 'img-fluid')
        .card-footer
          = link_to('Events',
                    events_path(trailing_slash: true),
                    class: 'btn btn-block btn-outline-primary')

.py-5
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-6
        %h1.py-3.text-center Be a Shriner. Impact the Future.
        %p.lead
          When you become a Shriner, you become part of a brotherhood of men committed to family,
          engaged in ongoing personal growth, and providing care for children and families in need.
        .d-flex.justify-content-center
          = link_to('Become a Shriner',
                    'https://www.beashrinernow.com',
                    class: 'btn btn-lg btn-danger mt-3 mb-5 mb-md-3')
      .col-md-6
        .embed-responsive.embed-responsive-16by9
          %iframe.embed-responsive-item{:allow => "accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture", :allowfullscreen => "", :frameborder => "0", :src => "https://www.youtube.com/embed/oobAw14Dj5o"}
